---
title: Seared Salmon and Lemony Lentil Bowl with Spinach, Sweet Potato and Feta Crema
description: Golden seared salmon fillets get a flavour boost from a garlicky feta cheese sauce and sit atop a bed of lemony lentils, roasted sweet potatoes and ever-so-slightly wilted baby spinach. Eat until your heart's content with this calorie-conscious bowl.

